    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729140/extras/c5b550050faaef0d1da128894488eec5.poster.avif?t=1761601783\" width=800 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729140/extras/c5b550050faaef0d1da128894488eec5.webm?t=1761601783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729140/extras/c5b550050faaef0d1da128894488eec5.mp4?t=1761601783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款1-4人合作生存恐怖游戏，真正的恐怖从上班开始。使用监控摄像头、运动传感器等清理、整理并控制危险生物。赚取薪水，升级你的工具并捕获它们——因为没有人会替你做。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729140/extras/d7b82eda374b0e4265eac332bd9237a5.avif?t=1761601783\" width=640 height=89 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729140/extras/1ddfc1aeed31c7834be004a54aed8c75.poster.avif?t=1761601783\" width=800 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729140/extras/1ddfc1aeed31c7834be004a54aed8c75.webm?t=1761601783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729140/extras/1ddfc1aeed31c7834be004a54aed8c75.mp4?t=1761601783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与朋友一起工作。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Hired 2 Die》是一款最多可支持4名玩家的合作生存恐怖游戏，其他世界的扭曲生物在工作场所游荡，成为危险的生物和奇怪的异常现象。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729140/extras/51333155ffeb685adbd408e73779fec7.avif?t=1761601783\" width=640 height=89 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729140/extras/ba131c733bf412592ab894373e74390f.poster.avif?t=1761601783\" width=800 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729140/extras/ba131c733bf412592ab894373e74390f.webm?t=1761601783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729140/extras/ba131c733bf412592ab894373e74390f.mp4?t=1761601783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>恐怖从上班开始.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你被神秘的Intersection公司雇佣。清理垃圾、拖地并悄悄整理环境，以免吸引扭曲生物。  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729140/extras/b6105b74540022211aa4fbe34b7eb20e.avif?t=1761601783\" width=640 height=89 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729140/extras/2f6785474f440282a7ea4db034c5979b.poster.avif?t=1761601783\" width=800 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729140/extras/2f6785474f440282a7ea4db034c5979b.webm?t=1761601783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729140/extras/2f6785474f440282a7ea4db034c5979b.mp4?t=1761601783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>逃跑是不够的，你需要捕获扭曲生物。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用监控摄像头、远程门、运动传感器和其他Intersection设备来确保有效捕获，冒着生命危险完成任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729140/extras/606d372fedb4a33ba879b0a78d46427a.avif?t=1761601783\" width=640 height=89 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729140/extras/b0539dd8aa0b77123b53213b97b85ec1.poster.avif?t=1761601783\" width=800 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729140/extras/b0539dd8aa0b77123b53213b97b85ec1.webm?t=1761601783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729140/extras/b0539dd8aa0b77123b53213b97b85ec1.mp4?t=1761601783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>室内设计不仅仅是为了美观!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用你的辛苦钱购买异常家具，为未来的任务提供增益。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729140/extras/3110b4a8aa9046347ac873ee33f24e99.avif?t=1761601783\" width=640 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>单人模式和合作模式：</strong> 游戏针对单人玩家和团队进行了不同的设计。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>进阶玩法：</strong> 即使是最简单的任务也是永久性的，并将在未来的合同中提供帮助。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>近距离语音聊天：</strong> 使用安全系统和对讲机与您的同事沟通和计划，但要小心，它们在听。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>保持交流，确保安全：</strong> 与您的朋友协调，使用说明手册修复复杂系统。</p>",
